headline: 4 Utility Stocks to Buy From the Flourishing Electric Power Industry
summary: NEE, AEE, LNT and PNW are set to benefit from rising demand from a strong customer base and well-chalked-out capital expenditure to upgrade infrastructure and provide reliable services.
